			<div class="question">Question 1: Tell us something about yourself.(include your placed co.)</div>

			<div class="answer">Answer:I belong to Ranchi itself. From the very first day of college I started experiencing this place in a completely different form. BIT Mesra has found a place close to our hearts. Throughout the college life I enjoyed fooling around with friends after classes were over, having a cup of coffee at IC so as to wash away the stress of 8 to 5. My want to be surrounded by techno-freak people in the college landed me at Robolution. From the day I got selected in the prestigious club, things became even more joyful ! Rushing to arena in evening and spending hours there working with superb seniors and friends, cycling back to hostels in chilling winter nights etc etc.. are the things which we are gonna always cherish. In third yr. I was made the Captain of Robolution and it was a completly diff. experience. I am currently working at Steradian Semiconductors where I'm part of the team doing development & validation of radar system software.</div>
