			<div class="question">Question 6:How being a part of Robolution helped you in gaining an edge over other candidates?</div>
			<div class="answer">Answer:Working on the stuffs we do at Robolution has infused a great amount of patient, compassion in me and the fantastic hardware projects toned my understanding about programing in such a way that nothing else could have done. Being a part of Robolution, we have been into situations where few seconds could have made months of hardwork & sacrifice worthless. Every project which I've done at Robolution had some cool innovative modifications in it. Robolution has made us ready to face even the most difficult technical challenges. Club's solid alumni network has always helped our members to have an edge in almost any company. We are in regular contact with our seniors be it 2k8 batch or 2k16 and our seniors have always helped us with guidance both technical & non-technical. Also the opportunity @ Steradian was available to me just because of our alumni network. Apart from practical expeience, our members are well versed in course subjects too and we are proud to have one of the most capable students of the college as our "family members".

			</div>
